## Private Member Functions

### expandBuildPairF64() {#a1047aeadf5e873545bd65d18eeac7a78}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>bool ExpandPseudo::expandBuildPairF64 (<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinebasicblock">MachineBasicBlock</a> &amp; MBB, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinebasicblock/#ae34c996b58df9b9ce6695a0c8b70c533">MachineBasicBlock::iterator</a> I, bool FP64) const</>}>
This method expands the same instruction that <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mipsseinstrinfo">MipsSEInstrInfo</a>:: expandBuildPairF64 does, for the case when ABI is fpxx and mthc1 is not available and the case where the ABI is FP64A.

It is implemented here because frame indexes are eliminated before <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mipsseinstrinfo">MipsSEInstrInfo</a>:: expandBuildPairF64 is called.
